[32m│[0m 3. Protocol 0 with `os.system('rm decoy.txt')`                               [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 4. Protocol 0 with `__builtin__.eval()`                                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 5. Protocol 0 with `subprocess.check_output()`                               [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 6. Protocol 0 with `builtins.exec()`                                         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 7. Protocol 4 with `builtins.exec()`                                         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m All payloads were accepted (HTTP 200 OK), but subsequent GET requests        [32m│[0m
